          <p class="summary-text">
            A highly motivated and passionate Full Stack MERN Developer with a strong academic background in BCA and MCA. Skilled in building dynamic, responsive, and user-centric web applications using modern technologies. Experienced in both frontend and backend development with a focus on performance, scalability, and clean code practices. Adept at problem-solving, API integration, and developing real-world projects. Eager to contribute to innovative teams and continuously enhance technical expertise.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
