              <span>React.js</span>
              <span>Node.js</span>
              <span>Express.js</span>
              <span>AI API</span>
            </div>
            <h3>AI Mockmate</h3>
            <p>An intelligent interview preparation platform designed to simulate real-time interview experiences. It provides AI-generated questions based on different domains and evaluates user responses to improve communication, technical knowledge, and confidence.</p>
            <div class="project-links">
              <a href="#" class="btn-project btn-project-primary"><i class="fa-solid fa-play"></i> Live Demo</a>
              <a href="#" class="btn-project btn-project-outline"><i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i> Codebase</a>
